{"tid":40514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李國章指示威者非常激動粗魯：我好驚呀！","createTime":"2016-12-15T08:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T10:03:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3cc4dead7e55814f7884d70660264b1d76cf8dc","tid":40514,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gm9yyvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgm9yyvH.jpg&h=8a0386a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港大校委會今年1月決定延遲成立研究港大管治的專組，會後校委會主席李國章等人被學生包圍，時任學生會會長馮敬恩及外務副會長李峯琦被起訴。馮敬恩今承認刑事毁壞和企圖強行進入兩罪，但否認其餘控罪。<br />\n<br />\n下午出庭作供的李國章供稱，當日他與港大校長馬斐森等在保安人鏈護送下離開大樓，門外有很多人叫口號和講粗口，馮敬恩更高叫：「唔好畀佢走！唔好畀李國章走！隊冧佢！隊冧佢！」李國章形容示威者「非常之激動，非常之粗魯」，令他「非常驚」，擔心會有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n李國章解釋，馮敬恩曾多於一次這樣叫，使印象深刻，這是他第一次被人用武力拉住，「嗌話要隊冧我」，令他感到有生命危險。李國章認為馮是在煽動示威者攻擊他，認為他是「主謀」。主控追問李國章當時有何感覺，李說：「我好驚呀！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161215/s00001/1481789044264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161215%2Fs00001%2F1481789044264&d=UzWHiFDZ68nYT9RT6v2vLwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f7e37346\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161215%2Fs00001%2F1481789044264&h=ecf930a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161215/s00001/1481789044264</a>"},{"pid":"da340936c43e4965d6b4b56ddbf54ef707a529c6","tid":40514,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a59beb5393862fb26904720ff2484170f6874a1","tid":40514,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0Zd3B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0Zd3B.gif&h=8136ec17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1cdf7a5369b9f3f78e3b6ebc8f44f542b02f551","tid":40514,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512e5388646a28579e8775e7741631315deb167d","tid":40514,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"驚你老母"},{"pid":"62347e930520a8b83b331e09cc814b176ee9a98a","tid":40514,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1c5d7208f0e08f9d169840bf07a2a171f5bb3a","tid":40514,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vr5U955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVr5U955.jpg&h=e8d1bc38&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}